info.author: sifter
info.description: This Program contains a "Server" class that will query gaming servers that use the Gamespy4 (UT3) protocol. It returns a dictionary of server info, ie; hostname, maxplayers, numplayers etc. , and a list of players as Player objects which is also  an included class in this program.
info.keywords: gamespy arma2 DAYZ minecraft gamespy4 python3 ut3

info.name: GameSpy4Query_Python3
info.summary: Server object to query game servers using the Gamespy4 Protocol or UT3.
info.html_description: This Program contains a “Server” class that will query gaming servers that use the Gamespy4 (UT3) protocol. It returns a dictionary of server info, ie; hostname, maxplayers, numplayers etc. , and a list of players as Player objects which is also an included class in this program.
